## Upload Instructions

1. Export each image as PNG or JPEG
2. Verify dimensions: exactly 1600 x 1600 pixels
3. Check file size: under 2MB per image
4. Name files exactly as listed above
5. Upload to this folder
6. Run quality checks from `05_documentation/quality_checklist.md`